---------------- add column to table after installed it in DB ----------------

- php artisan make:migration add_age_to_users
					  |           \
			     < name of column >   < name of table >
it will create new file and we will add column inside up func in it like that

-$table -> string ("age")->after("name") 							

then do :  php artisan migrate
to delete column 

- php artisan make:migration drop_age_to_users
					     |           \
			        < name of column >   < name of table >
inside down function in drop file

- $table -> dropColumn ("age");